headline: Paycom price target raised to $210 from $190 at Mizuho
summary: Mizuho analyst Siti Panigrahi raised the firm’s price target on Paycom (PAYC) to $210 from $190 and keeps a Neutral rating on the shares as part of a 2025 outlook for the software group. The firm increased price targets on several companies, largely a reflection of recent increases in comp multiples.
